  <brief_title>Quality of Life for Subjects Receiving Androgen Deprivation Therapy and Have a Doubling in PSA of Either Less Than or Greater Than 1 Year</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-Label, Phase ll Trial Comparing FACT-P Scores For Subjects Who Are Indicated To Receive Androgen Deprivation Therapy And Have A Doubling In PSA Post Curative Therapy Of Either Less Than Or Greater Than One Year</official_title>
