  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate if there is a difference in quality of life (as
      measured by FACT-P) in patients treated with androgen deprivation therapy (ADT) for
      biochemical failure (PSA recurrence) following surgery or radiation for prostate cancer
      depending on when ADT is initiated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
